{"title":"照相","authors":["李彤"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":2,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"照相"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王明义　马一丹  作画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李彤　配诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用镜头立下一个盟约——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把笑靥交给红花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和花后那片胸脯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（现在这张底片经过几番"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲洗会是什么模样？）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕新的征衣被战火撕破"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自有满襟的小花去补缀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再用嘴唇来熨平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用快门记下一个誓言——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭着古老的石板路起誓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭着风蚀雨刷的木板壁起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭着还没有见过的云影波"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光起誓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（背景布上的画在这一瞬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"间里变成真的）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每夜的同一个时刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让咱俩都唱一遍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《十五的月亮》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}